WEBVTT

00:00:02.040 --> 00:00:03.776
Vanessa Garrison: I am Vanessa,

00:00:03.800 --> 00:00:05.416
daughter of Annette,

00:00:05.440 --> 00:00:07.216
daughter of Olympia,

00:00:07.240 --> 00:00:08.776
daughter of Melvina,

00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:12.096
daughter of Katie, born 1878,

00:00:12.120 --> 00:00:13.880
Parish County, Louisiana.

00:00:14.600 --> 00:00:16.496
T. Morgan Dixon: And my name is Morgan,

00:00:16.520 --> 00:00:19.256
daughter of Carol,
daughter of Letha, daughter of Willie,

00:00:19.280 --> 00:00:23.656
daughter of Sarah,
born 1849 in Bardstown, Kentucky.

00:00:23.680 --> 00:00:25.696
VG: And in the tradition of our families,

00:00:25.720 --> 00:00:29.016
the great oral tradition
of almost every Black church we know

00:00:29.040 --> 00:00:32.936
honoring the culture
from which we draw so much power,